name: Strip-Tease
comments: Nico starred in the film "Strip-Tease" (her first lead role) whereas Gainsbourg wrote the soundtrack and also appeared in a cameo as a piano player. They recorded the theme song for the movie, but they were reportedly unhappy with the results, thus the recording remained unreleased until 2001. Eventually, the song was recorded by Juliette Gréco.
